Exception Handling

ways to handle exception
I)try-catch blocks
ii)throws key words


Types of exception
I)checked exception
ii)Unchecked exception
iii)Error


Unchecked exception :I) exception not checked by compiler.
ii)child class of Run time exception.

checked exception: I) exception checked by compiler.
ii)child class of exception


*)whether it is checked or unchecked exception , it runs at run time.

Error
I)lack of system resource are the main cause.
ii)unchecked types.
iii)not possible to handle.
Example : system out of memory.



